title: Social Club Discography 2012-2013 (7 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SOCIAL CLUB DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 7 releases...

 * 2012 - Misfit
 * 2012 - Misfit B-Sides
 * 2012 - Royale Deluxe
 * 2012 - SCMGWP
 * 2013 - Animal Kingdom - Single
 * 2013 - Rejects EP
 * 2013 - Summer Of George

Social Club is a movement dedicated to expressing honesty and hope in Jesus Christ. Our Vision: is to bring courage to people struggling with depression, insecurity, and sadness by investing into trusted leaders in their local community.

Blessings,
TorrentTracts - September 2013
